<lb n="0820b18" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0820b19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0820b20" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 37 [No. 27(51), No. 36]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0820b21" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說緣本致經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0820b22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0820b23" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0820005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人名〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0820005"><lem wit="【大】">人名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&lac;</rdg></app>今附東晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0820b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820b2401">聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。佛
<lb n="0820b25" ed="T"/>告諸比丘。愛訒<note n="0820006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">深＝染【三】</note><note n="0820006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">深＝染【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820006"><lem wit="【大】">深</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">染</rdg></app>有榮色未起為纏沒住亦
<lb n="0820b26" ed="T"/>有本栽。非無緣致愛有耽荒本致熟在狂醉
<lb n="0820b27" ed="T"/>為受不明觀解。是名癡本。</p>
<lb n="0820b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820b2801">癡緣所生亦為有本。何等為本。眩曜色聲五
<lb n="0820b29" ed="T"/>蓋馳惑。斯生癡本矣。</p>
<pb n="0820c" id="T01.0037.0820c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0820c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c0101">五蓋蔽冥致影沈吟亦為有本。何等為本。三
<lb n="0820c02" ed="T"/><note n="0820007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡種＝種惡【明】</note><app n="0820007"><lem wit="【大】">惡種</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">種惡</rdg></app>牽斯謂為本。</p>
<lb n="0820c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c0301">三惡栽習亦為有本。何等為本。不攝根識斯
<lb n="0820c04" ed="T"/>亦為本。</p>
<lb n="0820c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c0501">不攝根識緣致有本。何等為本。謂非所應念
<lb n="0820c06" ed="T"/>專<note n="0820008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">候＝念【三】</note><note n="0820008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">候＝念【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820008"><lem wit="【大】">候</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">念</rdg></app>不已。斯謂本也。非應所念。亦從本緣
<lb n="0820c07" ed="T"/>不為無本。何等為本。不從正信<note n="0820009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迷＝述【三】</note><note n="0820009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迷＝述【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820009"><lem wit="【大】">迷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">述</rdg></app>於所向。
<lb n="0820c08" ed="T"/>斯謂本也。不信從謬亦有緣致。非為無本。何
<lb n="0820c09" ed="T"/>等為本。惡師所引非法聽受。斯謂為本。非正
<lb n="0820c10" ed="T"/>失聽亦有緣本。何等為本。違背賢聖英&CB01842;之
<lb n="0820c11" ed="T"/>聚。斯謂為本。</p>
<lb n="0820c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c1201">乖錯賢&CB01842;緣致<note n="0820010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">違＝墜【三】</note><note n="0820010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">違＝墜【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820010"><lem wit="【大】">違</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">墜</rdg></app>背亦。為有本。何等為本。
<lb n="0820c13" ed="T"/>失於戴仰虛心集樂。斯<note n="0820011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謂＝為【明】</note><app n="0820011"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">為</rdg></app>本矣。如是比丘。
<lb n="0820c14" ed="T"/>夫失賢眾清高之聚。身口意行視聽惑滿。胸
<lb n="0820c15" ed="T"/>心閉塞矣。以非法見信向毀矣。正道負背則
<lb n="0820c16" ed="T"/>邪見增。邪<note n="0820012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔見〕－【三】</note><note n="0820012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔見〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820012"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>增則內攝喪。內攝喪則三惡興
<lb n="0820c17" ed="T"/>恣。三惡興恣則五蓋盈滿。五蓋盈滿則癡本
<lb n="0820c18" ed="T"/>足。癡本足則愛受盛。以斯轉種增著<note n="0820013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">猗＝倚【三】</note><note n="0820013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">猗＝倚【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820013"><lem wit="【大】">猗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">倚</rdg></app>有塵
<lb n="0820c19" ed="T"/>染無際矣。</p>
<lb n="0820c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c2001">度世明慧昇于脫要。亦為有本。何謂度世智
<lb n="0820c21" ed="T"/>慧解脫之本。七覺<note n="0820014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法妙＝妙法【三】</note><note n="0820014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法妙＝妙法【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820014"><lem wit="【大】">法妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">妙法</rdg></app>。謂為致本。</p>
<lb n="0820c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c2201">七覺鏡照亦為有本。何等為本。謂四意止。斯
<lb n="0820c23" ed="T"/>則覺本。四意靜止由從有本。非無有本。其義
<lb n="0820c24" ed="T"/>焉在。謂清淨潔妙。其行在三。</p>
<lb n="0820c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c2501">三清淨行亦為有本。非無有本。本義<note n="0820015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝謂【明】＊</note><app n="0820015"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">謂</rdg></app>何。
<lb n="0820c26" ed="T"/>謂守攝諸根。斯則為本。</p>
<lb n="0820c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c2701">守攝諸根亦為有本。非無有本。本義為何。謂
<lb n="0820c28" ed="T"/>鏡<note n="0820016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鑑＝攬【三】</note><note n="0820016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鑑＝攬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0820016"><lem wit="【大】">鑑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">攬</rdg></app>玄照。斯為本念矣。</p>
<lb n="0820c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0820c2901">本念照往亦為有本。緣致入正。何等為本。本
<pb n="0821a" id="T01.0037.0821a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0821a01" ed="T"/>念造勝。謂之樹信。</p>
<lb n="0821a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0821a0201">信亦有本不為無本。何等信本。謂多聞經道
<lb n="0821a03" ed="T"/>次第典要。斯謂為本。</p>
<lb n="0821a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0821a0401">聞於經法亦<app source="0820015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">謂</rdg></app>有本不為無本。何等聞法。謂
<lb n="0821a05" ed="T"/>賢行澄清業真者也。</p>
<lb n="0821a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0821a0601">賢者<note n="0821001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">清淨＝淳靜【三】</note><note n="0821001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">清淨＝淳靜【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0821001"><lem wit="【大】">清淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">淳靜</rdg></app>。亦為有本。何等為本。謂&CB01842;行清
<lb n="0821a07" ed="T"/>真潔白之聚。</p>
<lb n="0821a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0821a0801">如是比丘。賢者集勝依附明哲。奉事多聞能
<lb n="0821a09" ed="T"/>致信本。信本已立便得正念。正念已樹守攝
<lb n="0821a10" ed="T"/>諸根。根守已建登三行淨。已三清淨便四意
<lb n="0821a11" ed="T"/>止。四意止立便七覺意。七覺意成立。是即無
<lb n="0821a12" ed="T"/>為解脫度世。佛說如是。弟子<note n="0821002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝奉【明】</note><app n="0821002"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">奉</rdg></app>行。</p>
<lb n="0821a13" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說緣本致經</jhead></juan>
</div1></body></text></TEI.2>